# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:（投資、賭博或做生意）當虧本嘅時候，即刻賣出或者停止，以免蝕更多錢（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop a loss
<eg>
yue:佢買咗隻股票跌咗好多，所以即刻止蝕。 (keoi5 maai5 zo2 gwo3 zing3 gup3 dik1, jat1 zo2 hou2 do1, so2 ji5 gik1 gik1 zi2 sik6.)
eng:He bought a stock that fell a lot, so he immediately cut his losses.

<eg>
yue:做生意思唔好貪心，見勢色唔對就要快啲止蝕。 (zou6 saang1 ji1 si1 m4 hou2 taam1 sam1, gin3 sai3 sik6 m4 deoi3 zau6 jiu4 faai3 di1 zi2 sik6.)
eng:When doing business, don't be too greedy; if the situation looks wrong, you must cut losses quickly. [end of text]


